This paper deals with natural language processing and neural networks, which are typically categorized under cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the use of LSTM-style gating, which is a popular technique in the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper presents an artificial learning task, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE) and computer vision (cs.CV).
